  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Petrol ship delayed indefinitely",
      "author": "",
      "body_lines": [
        "The ship carrying 40,000 metric tons of 92 octane petrol will be further delayed, Power and Energy Minister Kanchana Wijesekera said this afternoon (24).",
        "The Minister said that the supplier had informed the Ceylon Petroleum Corporation that the ship would arrive today and that the Ceylon Petroleum Corporation had been informed that it would be further delayed.",
        "The Minister said that the date of the ship's arrival in Sri Lanka would be announced later, adding that he regretted the delay of the ship and the announcements made that it would arrive today."
      ],
